FlashFace: The perfect app for Police with the perfect criminal datatbase

FlashFace is a police database app with criminal matching software which stores the data of previously caught criminals along with their current status and matches images of suspects with its database to see whether the suspect was a previous criminal or not.

Get started Github Star

Perfect for an online criminal datbase

The app has been built using a django REST API which has sqlite database already present
